Court of Massachusetts,

877
00:52:29,940 --> 00:52:31,660
two months from tomorrow.

878
00:52:31,660 --> 00:52:34,373
Bond is set in the amount of $500,000.

879
00:52:35,300 --> 00:52:37,850
If in fact, you do decide to post bail,

880
00:52:37,850 --> 00:52:39,910
you are prohibited by
law to travel outside

881
00:52:39,910 --> 00:52:41,800
the state of Illinois.

