00:52:41,800 --> 00:52:43,490
This interdiction will be lifted

883
00:52:43,490 --> 00:52:45,270
one week prior to your trial

884
00:52:45,270 --> 00:52:47,210
to allow you enough time to transition

885
00:52:47,210 --> 00:52:48,900
to the state of Massachusetts.

886
00:52:48,900 --> 00:52:50,730
In which your attorney must notify

887
00:52:50,730 --> 00:52:52,780
the court before making any arrangements.

888
00:52:53,720 --> 00:52:54,810
Do you understand?

889
00:52:54,810 --> 00:52:56,360
- Yes, Your Honor.

890
00:52:56,360 --> 00:53:00,409
- [Judge] Next case, State
of Illinois versus Hernandez.

