two or three hours,

995
00:59:38,490 --> 00:59:39,683
deliberations and all.

996
00:59:41,040 --> 00:59:43,460
- So you're saying we
don't stand a chance?

997
00:59:43,460 --> 00:59:44,293
- In hell.

998
00:59:45,980 --> 00:59:47,580
I mean, any reputable law firm

999
00:59:47,580 --> 00:59:48,920
would be leery of a case like this.

1000
00:59:48,920 --> 00:59:51,023
You need a damn good one to represent you.

1001
00:59:52,540 --> 00:59:55,660
I think you're better off
settling for a plea bargain.

1002
00:59:55,660 --> 00:59:58,520
That is, if the prosecution
is charitable enough

1003
00:59:58,520 --> 00:59:59,727
to extend you one.

1004
01:00:04,370 --> 01:00:05,203
- A plea bargain?

1005
01:00:05,203 --> 01:00:06,893
That's the advice you have for me?

1006
01:00:07,950 --> 01:00:09,453
- It's complicated, Audrey.

1007
01:00:10,750 --> 01:00:15,050
- I understand that, but it's
a lot more complicated for me.

1008
01:00:15,050 --> 01:00:16,680
My family is at stake.

1009
01:00:16,680 --> 01:00:18,843
I could lose my son.

1010
01:00:20,800 --> 01:00:24,140
- Well technically, he isn't your son.

1011
01:00:24,140 --> 01:00:26,010
See, that's what makes your attempt

1012
01:00:26,010 --> 01:00:28,403
to hold onto him legally impossible.

1013
01:00:32,090 --> 01:00:35,060
Do you even know who
or where the father is?

1014
01:00:35,060 --> 01:00:36,100
He'd be next of kin,

1015
01:00:36,100 --> 01:00:38,700
so by law, he'd be
Brian's rightful guardian.

1016
01:00:38,700 --> 01:00:40,700
- I mean, it could be any number of men.

1017
01:00:41,600 --> 01:00:42,513
- Yeah, possibly.

1018
01:00:44,200 --> 01:00:46,860
But I don't think you can fight this one.

1019
01:00:46,860 --> 01:00:50,300
So my advice is to go home,

1020
01:00:50,300 --> 01:00:51,820
explain everything to the kid,

1021
01:00:51,820 --> 01:00:54,443
and send him to his
grandparents in Boston.

1022
01:00:55,650 --> 01:00:59,253
And hope for leniency when the
judge decides your sentence.

1023
01:01:09,530 --> 01:01:11,230
Please tell me you didn't know anything

1024
01:01:11,230 --> 01:01:13,023
about this before you married her?

1025
01:01:15,270 --> 01:01:17,220
All things considered,
your legal guardianship

1026
01:01:17,220 --> 01:01:18,470
